HEADWORD: Deliverer
<hw>De*liv"er*er</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>One
who delivers or rescues; a preserver.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>One who relates or communicates.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

